query:
index=someindex sourcetype=somesourcetype
| eval http_status_num = tonumber(payload.http_status)
| eval HTTP_Category = if(http_status_num >= 200 AND http_status_num < 300, "200-299",
if(http_status_num >= 300 AND http_status_num < 400, "300-399",
if(http_status_num >= 400 AND http_status_num < 500, "400-499",
if(http_status_num >= 500 AND http_status_num < 600, "500-599", "Other"))))
| stats count by HTTP_Category
